<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Confirmation - Plenty Value</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Segoe UI, Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { background: #001845; color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { padding: 40px; color: #333; }
    .content p { margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.6; }
    .order-details { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 10px 0; }
    .footer { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Plenty Value</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Thank you for your purchase!</p>
      <p>Your order has been confirmed. Here are the details:</p>
      <div class="order-details">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <strong>Order Number:</strong>
          <span>{{ order.orderNumber }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <strong>Product:</strong>
          <span>{{ order.productName }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <strong>Amount:</strong>
          <span>${{ order.amount }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <strong>Status:</strong>
          <span>{{ order.status }}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>We appreciate your business and hope you enjoy your purchase!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Plenty Value. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
